dji.sdk.api.Battery

Class DJIBatteryProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.Battery.DJIBatteryProperty

  • public class DJIBatteryProperty
extends java.lang.Object

    DJI Battery Property Class

    This class is a set of battery information including battery temperature, current and voltage. The instance of DJIBatteryProperty will be used in the callback functions and transfer the information from aircraft.
    Version:
    V2.4.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
